	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Would it be possible to hack Contra japaneese (Gryzor) to use a MMC3 mapper instead of VRC4 and to be programmed on a TLROM card ?
<br />Is there any accurate VRC4 doccuments ?

		

		</td>
