<br />Thanks for correcting/clarifyng. Gryzor is the name of the unoficial engish translation from the japaneese one, right ? I also seen that Gryzor was the name of the arcade counterpart of Contra. So I think they renamed it for that reason ? At least the responsable to name roms under goodnes standards did wrong here.
